description:
We often think of unity when it comes to the Church, but what of the diversity of the Church–even in the very gifts and talents we each have as individuals?  #Webelieve the Church is blessed with many parts and people with many talents and gifts, connected through the Spirit, but as individual as our fingerprints. #Biblestudy #AdventistBeliefs 
For the full video, paste the link into your browser: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t1A3-qtY1ek
fulltitle: Unity in the Body of Christ
